Definitely! You simply create a partial like so -

```&lt;div&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;Header&lt;/h1&gt;
{% block modules %}{% endblock %}
&lt;/div&gt;```

And then your main content template (the one you are actually using)

```{% extends "/layouts/header.html" %}

{% block modules %}
{%  module "module_123456789" 
label="Content"      
no_wrapper='True'
path="/modules/content" %}
{% endblock %}```
